<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="1020000000t" end="1028330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">Amir.</p>
<p begin="2151020000t" end="2193100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">Syarat untuk seseorang menjadi pemimpin</p>
<p begin="2194770000t" end="2235600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">yang membimbing manusia ke jalan Allah</p>
<p begin="2241430000t" end="2259350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">ialah sabar.</p>
<p begin="2278520000t" end="2343100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">Hendaklah dia bersabar demi meneruskan<br/>perjuangan dan tanggungjawab</p>
<p begin="2344350000t" end="2369350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">untuk membela Islam.</p>
<p begin="2375600000t" end="2405600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">Berpesan-pesan dengan kebenaran</p>
<p begin="2408930000t" end="2446430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">dan berpesan-pesan dengan kesabaran.</p>
<p begin="2464770000t" end="2480600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">Bukan senang,</p>
<p begin="2486020000t" end="2520180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">hendak menjadi seorang pendakwah</p>
<p begin="2526850000t" end="2560600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">yang betul-betul ikhlas, Salmah.</p>
<p begin="2566020000t" end="2596020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">Mudah-mudahan, Adam istiqamah.</p>
<p begin="2596850000t" end="2631020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">Saya bukan nak pertikaikan<br/>perjuangan Adam, Bang.</p>
<p begin="2636430000t" end="2676430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">Tapi sebagai Mak,<br/>saya takut peristiwa lama berulang lagi.</p>
<p begin="2680180000t" end="2707680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">Pasal dengki dan dendam orang pada Adam,</p>
<p begin="2708520000t" end="2735600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">kita kehilangan menantu dan cucu kita.</p>
<p begin="2761850000t" end="2778520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">Maafkan Sakinah, Ayah.</p>
<p begin="2787920000t" end="2828750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">Sakinah tak tahu apa yang Sakinah<br/>patut buat lagi untuk pulihkan Ayah.</p>
<p begin="2832270000t" end="2847270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">Sakinah tak mampu.</p>
<p begin="2848930000t" end="2868520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">Tak ada siapa yang sanggup tolong kita.</p>
<p begin="2905600000t" end="2931020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">Mudah-mudahan, Allah akan pulihkan Ayah</p>
<p begin="2946020000t" end="2976430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">sihat kembali, kerap bercakap macam dulu.</p>
<p begin="3155600000t" end="3176850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">Cepatlah makan. Mak tahu Aina lapar.</p>
<p begin="3179770000t" end="3210600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">Sampai bila Aina kena makan<br/>benda yang sama ni tiap-tiap hari?</p>
<p begin="3214350000t" end="3250600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">Insya Allah, esok Mak pergi pekan<br/>beli apa yang Aina suka.</p>
<p begin="3262680000t" end="3272680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">Sudahlah.</p>
<p begin="3274770000t" end="3285180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">Mak suapkan.</p>
<p begin="3286430000t" end="3298100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">Mak tipu!</p>
<p begin="3323520000t" end="3354770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">Kenapa Mak bawa Atuk dan Aina<br/>duduk dalam hutan ini?</p>
<p begin="3356020000t" end="3373520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">Sampai bila kita perlu duduk sini?</p>
<p begin="3374350000t" end="3386020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">Aina, jangan biadap.</p>
<p begin="3389770000t" end="3408940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">Mak tak suka Aina tanya soalan itu.</p>
<p begin="3409770000t" end="3421020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">Tapi kenapa?</p>
<p begin="3421850000t" end="3431850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">Aina nak tahu!</p>
<p begin="3432680000t" end="3452270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">Satu hari nanti Aina akan tahu.</p>
<p begin="3453100000t" end="3494350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">Tapi bukan sekarang. Kita semua terpaksa<br/>tinggal sini, jauh daripada orang kampung.</p>
<p begin="3498100000t" end="3519350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">Mak buat semua ni sebab sayang Aina.</p>
<p begin="3525180000t" end="3537680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">Talbis Iblis.</p>
<p begin="3538520000t" end="3577680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">Iblis apabila ingin menyesatkan manusia.<br/>Dia akan melakukan Talbis.</p>
<p begin="3578930000t" end="3619350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">Talbis adalah</p>
<p begin="3623930000t" end="3653100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">Menzahirkan benda yang salah,<br/>perkara yang batil</p>
<p begin="3664770000t" end="3679350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">di dalam gambaran yang betul.</p>
<p begin="3680180000t" end="3701020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">Iblis pandai dalam menyesatkan manusia.</p>
<p begin="3709350000t" end="3736020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">Sebab itulah ada golongan ilmuwan,<br/>orang-orang soleh</p>
<p begin="3736850000t" end="3761430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">yang tewas,<br/>terjerumus dalam belitan Iblis.</p>
<p begin="3762680000t" end="3791430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">Di dalam Al-Quran,<br/>Allah mengeji banyak kumpulan.</p>
<p begin="3793930000t" end="3836850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">Tapi kumpulan yang paling teruk Allah keji<br/>adalah para Ulama yang tidak amanah.</p>
<p begin="3879770000t" end="3900600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">Ia termasuk<br/>di kalangan orang-orang sesat.</p>
<p begin="3927680000t" end="3938510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">Allah samakan</p>
<p begin="3939350000t" end="3971430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">ulama yang mengharapkan habuan dunia<br/>seperti Anjing.</p>
<p begin="3997270000t" end="4014770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">Bandingan ulama seperti ini</p>
<p begin="4038100000t" end="4052270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">sama seperti anjing.</p>
<p begin="4081020000t" end="4095600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">Kita berlindung kepada Allah.</p>
<p begin="4210600000t" end="4228930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">Bertaubatlah Abuja!</p>
<p begin="4231850000t" end="4251020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">Takutlah kau pada Allah!</p>
<p begin="4251430000t" end="4297270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">Sampai bila kau nak bunuh semua orang<br/>yang nak tegakkan agama Allah?</p>
<p begin="4298930000t" end="4322260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">Engkau percayakan Allah dan Rasul.</p>
<p begin="4326430000t" end="4353520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">Tapi kenapa kau tak percayakan<br/>aku dan ajaran aku?</p>
<p begin="4354350000t" end="4374350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">Aku juga berjuang di jalan Allah.</p>
<p begin="4375180000t" end="4395180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">Kau dusta pada Al-Quran!</p>
<p begin="4396020000t" end="4413930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">Kau dustakan hadis!</p>
<p begin="4414770000t" end="4431850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">Apa yang kau tahu, Rahman?</p>
<p begin="4432680000t" end="4458100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">Kau nak beritahu Abuja munafik?<br/>Kau yang munafik!</p>
<p begin="4458930000t" end="4474770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">Jangan kau tentang Abuja.</p>
<p begin="4475600000t" end="4495180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">Terima saja ajaran kami, Rahman.</p>
<p begin="4496020000t" end="4524350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">Atau kau akan terima nasib<br/>seperti mayat-mayat itu!</p>
<p begin="4535180000t" end="4547680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">Kau takut, Rahman?</p>
<p begin="4548520000t" end="4574350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">Aku takut hanya pada Allah.</p>
<p begin="4575180000t" end="4592680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">Kau orang semua sesat!</p>
<p begin="4593930000t" end="4632270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">Tak ada sesiapa pun yang boleh menghalang<br/>orang lain untuk jadi pengikut aku.</p>
<p begin="4633520000t" end="4668930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">Orang macam kau wajib dimusuhi, diperangi!</p>
<p begin="4669770000t" end="4681020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">Engkau kafir!</p>
<p begin="4681850000t" end="4702680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">Aku takkan ikut ajaran kau.</p>
<p begin="4706430000t" end="4722270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">Aku tak akan ikut!</p>
<p begin="4757270000t" end="4786430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">Tiada Tuhan selain Allah.</p>
<p begin="4787270000t" end="4816430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">Muhammad Rasulullah!</p>
<p begin="4866430000t" end="4892270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al-Ikhlas, Ayat Satu</span></p>
<p begin="5118930000t" end="5132270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">Assalamualaikum Azhar.</p>
<p begin="5134770000t" end="5156020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">-Apa khabar?<br/>-Waalaikumussalam.</p>
<p begin="5156850000t" end="5169770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">Macam mana bisnes bot?</p>
<p begin="5171850000t" end="5198930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">Alhamdulillah.<br/>Pak Rahim nak pergi kampung seberang?</p>
<p begin="5199770000t" end="5213520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">Yalah.</p>
<p begin="5215600000t" end="5239770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">Dah lama tak jumpa Imam Malik.</p>
<p begin="5243520000t" end="5266020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">Apa khabar kawan aku tu?</p>
<p begin="5270600000t" end="5296430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">Ini, Sakinah anak dia.<br/>Masih tinggal dengan dia ke?</p>
<p begin="5297270000t" end="5318100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">Saya rasa, Pak Rahim balik sahajalah.</p>
<p begin="5326850000t" end="5354350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">Imam Malik dah lama<br/>berhenti jadi Imam di kampung saya.</p>
<p begin="5355600000t" end="5373100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">Berhenti jadi Imam?</p>
<p begin="5377270000t" end="5388520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">Sejak bila?</p>
<p begin="5394350000t" end="5409350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">Dia sakit ke, Azhar?</p>
<p begin="5418930000t" end="5429350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">Kenapa ni, Azhar?</p>
<p begin="5446850000t" end="5468100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">Kampung kami dah tak macam dulu,<br/>Pak Rahim.</p>
<p begin="5468930000t" end="5481430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">Dah banyak berubah.</p>
<p begin="5496020000t" end="5516850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">Saya nak cerita ni pun susah.</p>
<p begin="5518100000t" end="5536020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">Saya dah lama tak nampak Imam.</p>
<p begin="5536850000t" end="5558520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">Kampung kamu dah tak macam dulu?</p>
<p begin="5565600000t" end="5583100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">Apa maksud kamu ini?</p>
<p begin="5650600000t" end="5669770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">Sakinah, tunggu!</p>
<p begin="5726020000t" end="5756850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">Kesusahan yang kau dan keluarga kau<br/>lalui sekarang ini</p>
<p begin="5757680000t" end="5778520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">boleh berakhir sekelip mata saja.</p>
<p begin="5779770000t" end="5796850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">Kau boleh hidup bahagia.</p>
<p begin="5805180000t" end="5823520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">Ayah kau kembali sembuh.</p>
<p begin="5828520000t" end="5851850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">Dan setan iblis takkan kacau kau lagi.</p>
<p begin="5853520000t" end="5871020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">Cakaplah apa pun, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="5876430000t" end="5904770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">Hantarlah jin, syaitan,<br/>berapa banyak mana pun.</p>
<p begin="5914770000t" end="5932270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">Aku takkan berpaling dari Islam.</p>
<p begin="5935180000t" end="5952270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">Aku takkan ikut ajaran kau.</p>
<p begin="5955180000t" end="5980180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">Aku tak bodoh, <br/>mudah terperdaya dengan kau.</p>
<p begin="5981020000t" end="6002680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">Apa yang aku buat ni bukan kehendak aku.</p>
<p begin="6015180000t" end="6042680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">Tapi ilham dari Tuhan<br/>untuk sampaikan kebenaran!</p>
<p begin="6043520000t" end="6055180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">Kebenaran apa?</p>
<p begin="6057680000t" end="6073510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">Kau cuma bawa kesesatan.</p>
<p begin="6074350000t" end="6110600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">Ilham yang kau dapat tu daripada syaitan,<br/>bukan daripada Tuhan.</p>
<p begin="6111430000t" end="6147270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">Senang-senang kau kafirkan orang<br/>yang tak nak ikut ajaran sesat kau.</p>
<p begin="6148100000t" end="6175600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">Siapa aja yang berpaling dari aku<br/>memang kafir!</p>
<p begin="6179770000t" end="6206850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">Tak habis-habis buat bida'ah,<br/>dholalah, mazmumah!</p>
<p begin="6213930000t" end="6234770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">Termasuklah kau dan ayah kau itu.</p>
<p begin="6238100000t" end="6267270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">Sebab tu lah dia kena musibah!<br/>Balasan Tuhan!</p>
<p begin="6294770000t" end="6305180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">Tapi kau...</p>
<p begin="6314350000t" end="6362680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">aku masih bagi peluang<br/>untuk bertaubat dan jadi isteri aku.</p>
<p begin="6363520000t" end="6390600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">Jadi isteri<br/>atau hamba pemuas nafsu syaitan kau?</p>
<p begin="6391430000t" end="6430600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">Orang sesat macam kau lah yang <br/>buat agama rosak dan Islam disalah tafsir.</p>
<p begin="6773100000t" end="6783100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">Maria.</p>
<p begin="6804770000t" end="6815600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">Kenapa?</p>
<p begin="7326430000t" end="7338930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">Aku tak tahu lah, Man.</p>
<p begin="7348930000t" end="7370600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">Kenapa aku mimpi benda yang sama?</p>
<p begin="7383100000t" end="7418100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">Seolah-olah macam ada petanda<br/>kenapa aku asyik mimpi pasal arwah Maria.</p>
<p begin="7419770000t" end="7432270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">Petanda apa pulak Adam?</p>
<p begin="7433100000t" end="7443100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">Sudah-sudahlah itu.</p>
<p begin="7444350000t" end="7467270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">Semua dah jadi<br/>sejarah hitam dalam hidup kau.</p>
<p begin="7471430000t" end="7482270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">Insya Allah.</p>
<p begin="7498930000t" end="7525600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">Musibah macam itu takkan berulang lagi.</p>
<p begin="7538520000t" end="7549350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">Percayalah.</p>
<p begin="7568100000t" end="7592270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">Selagi nyawa dan roh<br/>belum sampai ke halkum,</p>
<p begin="7597680000t" end="7617270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">ujian dari Alllah takkan berhenti, Man.</p>
<p begin="7618930000t" end="7633930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">Apa yang berlaku itu,</p>
<p begin="7646020000t" end="7656850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">bukan pilihan kau.</p>
<p begin="7658100000t" end="7668100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">Kenapa?</p>
<p begin="7671430000t" end="7684770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">Kau rasa bersalah,</p>
<p begin="7690180000t" end="7700600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">atas arwah Maria?</p>
<p begin="7701430000t" end="7711430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">Entahlah, Man.</p>
<p begin="7722680000t" end="7759770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">Tapi apa yang pasti, aku rasa<br/>macam ada sesuatu yang masih belum selesai</p>
<p begin="7767680000t" end="7781020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">pasal kematian Maria dulu.</p>
<p begin="7818100000t" end="7846020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">Sesungguhnya, akulah ketua!</p>
<p begin="7856850000t" end="7887680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">Akulah pemimpin di antara kamu semua,</p>
<p begin="7888520000t" end="7925180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">kerana ketinggian darjat<br/>dan ketinggian maqam ku.</p>
<p begin="7928100000t" end="7975600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">Aku boleh tolong kamu semua<br/>untuk lebih faham al-Quran dan hadis.</p>
<p begin="7978100000t" end="8020600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">Jangan buat perkara bid'ah<br/>yang hanya menyusahkan hidup.</p>
<p begin="8021430000t" end="8050600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">Agama bukan pakai akal!</p>
<p begin="8060600000t" end="8092270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">Banyak lagi perkara ghaib<br/>yang kamu takkan faham</p>
<p begin="8093100000t" end="8124350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">Aku tahu siapa di kalangan kamu</p>
<p begin="8126850000t" end="8169350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">yang bakal bersama-sama aku<br/>berjalan di syurga!</p>
<p begin="8173930000t" end="8234350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">Aku mampu menilik nasib<br/>dan takdir setiap dari kamu.</p>
<p begin="8235180000t" end="8252680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">Berzikir!</p>
<p begin="8299770000t" end="8316430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">Zikir!</p>
<p begin="8326020000t" end="8363930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">Zikir! Terus ke syurga!</p>
<p begin="8613520000t" end="8627680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">Sakinah...</p>
<p begin="8754350000t" end="8766020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">Ayah?</p>
<p begin="9003520000t" end="9013520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">Mak.</p>
<p begin="9031850000t" end="9044350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">Ikut Aina!</p>
<p begin="9223520000t" end="9240600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">Aina buat apa di atas itu?</p>
<p begin="10059350000t" end="10069350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">Mak!</p>
<p begin="10164770000t" end="10183520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">-Mak!<br/>-Kenapa?</p>
<p begin="10203100000t" end="10226020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">-Atuk, Mak!<br/>-Kenapa dengan Atuk?</p>
<p begin="10226850000t" end="10259770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">Atuk kacau Aina! Atuk kacau Aina!</p>
<p begin="10337680000t" end="10347270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">Cepat, Aina!</p>
<p begin="10383930000t" end="10398100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">Sakinah...</p>
<p begin="10412680000t" end="10426850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">Tolong Ayah....</p>
<p begin="10443100000t" end="10461430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">Tolong Ayah, Sakinah...</p>
<p begin="10661430000t" end="10731430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al-A'la, Ayat Lima hingga Tujuh</span></p>
<p begin="10810600000t" end="10821430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">Siapa tu?</p>
<p begin="10920600000t" end="10930600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="10935600000t" end="10956430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">Aku perlu pertolongan kau, Azhar.</p>
<p begin="10964770000t" end="10977270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">Abuja dah melampau.</p>
<p begin="10992680000t" end="11017270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">Tolong keluarga aku dari<br/>terus diganggu syaitan.</p>
<p begin="11018100000t" end="11038520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">Selamatkan Ayah aku.</p>
<p begin="11060600000t" end="11074350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">Aku merayu dengan kau.</p>
<p begin="11085180000t" end="11098930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">Insya Allah, Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="11099770000t" end="11133520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">Aku ada kenal orang yang lebih layak<br/>untuk lawan sihir Abuja ini.</p>
<p begin="11380600000t" end="11393100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">Kenapa?</p>
<p begin="11400180000t" end="11431850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">Kenapa Tuhanmu tidak menjadikan<br/>semua orang beriman?</p>
<p begin="11448100000t" end="11464350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">Kenapa kau datang rumah aku ini?</p>
<p begin="11478520000t" end="11497270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">Semalam pun kau datang sini juga kan.</p>
<p begin="11498100000t" end="11513930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">Pergi jauh-jauh dengan kawan.</p>
<p begin="11514770000t" end="11530190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">Jawab sahaja pertanyaanku!</p>
<p begin="11535600000t" end="11545600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">Kenapa?</p>
<p begin="11546850000t" end="11571850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">Tuhan-mu tidak akan menyesatkan hamba-Nya.</p>
<p begin="11574770000t" end="11594770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">Allah tidak zalim pada hambanya.</p>
<p begin="11595600000t" end="11613100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">Hidayah milik Allah azza wajalla.</p>
<p begin="11613930000t" end="11636010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">Dia akan beri hidayah<br/>kepada yang carinya.</p>
<p begin="11637680000t" end="11659350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">Manis sekali kamu berbicara, Adam.</p>
<p begin="11661020000t" end="11683930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">Jiwamu memanggilku datang ke sini.</p>
<p begin="11686020000t" end="11714770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">Aku tahu, kamu kesunyian.</p>
<p begin="11719770000t" end="11733100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">Aku tak pernah sunyi.</p>
<p begin="11740180000t" end="11769770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">Tak pernah keseorangan,<br/>kerana sesungguhnya Allah itu dekat.</p>
<p begin="11770600000t" end="11784350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">Dia ada bersama dengan aku.</p>
<p begin="11785180000t" end="11816020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">Tuhan dekat dengan kamu? Kita juga dekat.</p>
<p begin="11818520000t" end="11855600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">Jadi apa bezanya? Bagaimana kamu<br/>bisa bilang yang kamu dekat dengan Tuhan?</p>
<p begin="11858520000t" end="11872270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">Apa kamu bisa lihat Tuhan?</p>
<p begin="11873100000t" end="11896430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">Ya. Setiap Muslim boleh melihat Allah.</p>
<p begin="11897270000t" end="11925600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">Dengan izin Allah,<br/>di akhirat nanti, bukan di dunia.</p>
<p begin="11926430000t" end="11954350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">Mudah-mudahan aku<br/>dan mukmin lain menjadi ahli syurga.</p>
<p begin="11957270000t" end="11989350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">Ahli syurga?<br/>Jangan terlalu yakin dulu kamu Adam.</p>
<p begin="11990180000t" end="12006010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">Perjalanan kamu masih jauh.</p>
<p begin="12007680000t" end="12022680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">Kita lihat sahaja nanti.</p>
<p begin="12094350000t" end="12126020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">Kenapa mesti Adam<br/>yang kena selesaikan masalah orang lain?</p>
<p begin="12126850000t" end="12150180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">Ada ramai lagi ustaz yang boleh pergi.</p>
<p begin="12151850000t" end="12213520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">Ini kan dah memang tugas dia mengubat<br/>orang sakit, tanggungjawab dia.</p>
<p begin="12221020000t" end="12232270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">Lagipun...</p>
<p begin="12241430000t" end="12284350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">yang sakit itu Imam Malik,<br/>kawan baik saya.</p>
<p begin="12286020000t" end="12299770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">Bukan nak halang kau, Adam.</p>
<p begin="12300600000t" end="12344770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">Tapi kalau benda ini menyusahkan<br/>hati Mak kau, elok tak payah.</p>
<p begin="12346020000t" end="12366020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">Baik kau jaga kebun dan ladang kau.</p>
<p begin="12368930000t" end="12393100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">Tak payah nak sibuk-sibuk hal orang lain.</p>
<p begin="12397270000t" end="12411430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">Buat apa nak susahkan diri?</p>
<p begin="12412270000t" end="12428930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">Saya tak yakin</p>
<p begin="12431020000t" end="12467270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">ada ustaz lain yang lebih berpengalaman<br/>untuk mengubat Imam Malik itu.</p>
<p begin="12468930000t" end="12490600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">Ikut apa yang Sakinah cerita kepada saya,</p>
<p begin="12492270000t" end="12506020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">teruk sakit bapanya itu.</p>
<p begin="12508520000t" end="12531020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">Sihir ini bukan boleh buat main-main tahu?</p>
<p begin="12532270000t" end="12548520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">Keselamatan anak aku macam mana?</p>
<p begin="12551020000t" end="12582270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">Kalau terjadi apa-apa pada Adam,<br/>kau nak tanggung ke, Azhar?</p>
<p begin="12583100000t" end="12604350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">Adam rasa elok pergi tengok Imam Malik.</p>
<p begin="12606020000t" end="12622270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">Kita tak tahu mungkin ni hikmah.</p>
<p begin="12637270000t" end="12673520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">Kau lebih pentingkan orang lain<br/>daripada perasaan Mak kau sendiri.</p>
<p begin="12686850000t" end="12706430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">Mak tidak akan izinkan kau pergi, Adam.</p>
<p begin="12721020000t" end="12736020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">Mak tidak akan izinkan.</p>
<p begin="12743520000t" end="12763520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">Bila Atuk akan baik, Mak?</p>
<p begin="12764350000t" end="12784350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">Atuk dah tak macam dulu lagi.</p>
<p begin="12786850000t" end="12820600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">Aina takutlah duduk rumah<br/>kalau Atuk terus macam itu.</p>
<p begin="12822680000t" end="12857270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">Mak tahu. Macam mana pun,<br/>Mak dan Aina perlu tolong Atuk sekarang.</p>
<p begin="12864350000t" end="12891850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">Insya Allah ada orang datang hari ini,<br/>tolong kita.</p>
<p begin="12977270000t" end="12985600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">Aina, lari!</p>
<p begin="12986430000t" end="12994770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">Pegang dia.</p>
<p begin="13002270000t" end="13020180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">Apa yang kau buat ini? Aina!</p>
<p begin="13034770000t" end="13047270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">Lepaskan anak aku!</p>
<p begin="13077270000t" end="13091850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">Lepaskan dia!</p>
<p begin="13099350000t" end="13134350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">Lepaskan aku! Jangan ambil Aina, Abuja!</p>
<p begin="13149350000t" end="13171850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">Jangan buat keluarga aku macam ini, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="13176850000t" end="13188520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">Bagi anak aku.</p>
<p begin="13189350000t" end="13209350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">Mungkin dengan cara ini sahaja...</p>
<p begin="13210180000t" end="13223930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">kau akan tunduk kepada aku.</p>
<p begin="13224770000t" end="13250180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">Terbuka hati kau untuk terima ajaran aku.</p>
<p begin="13254350000t" end="13272270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">Aku bukan bawa ajaran Syiah.</p>
<p begin="13273520000t" end="13291430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">Agama aku lebih suci.</p>
<p begin="13293100000t" end="13324770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">Aku tak pernah maki hamun<br/>para sahabat dan isteri Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="13325600000t" end="13353930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">Tak cukup ke kau buat bapa aku macam ini?</p>
<p begin="13358100000t" end="13377270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">Kau sihir dia sampai dia sakit!</p>
<p begin="13378930000t" end="13413100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">Sekarang anak aku pula?<br/>Lebih baik kau ambil darah aku!</p>
<p begin="13420180000t" end="13458100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">Bunuh saja aku!<br/>Bunuh aku, Abuja! Untuk kau puas!</p>
<p begin="13480180000t" end="13513100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">Kau satu-satunya manusia<br/>yang ingkar perintah-perintah Abuja.</p>
<p begin="13513930000t" end="13531020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">Kau bongkak, Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="13531850000t" end="13551850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">Bukan sahaja tak pandai berterima kasih</p>
<p begin="13553520000t" end="13580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">tapi kau hina ajaran kami.<br/>Kau hina Abuja!</p>
<p begin="13581430000t" end="13630600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">Darah kau sememangnya halal sebab dosa kau<br/>pada aku terlalu besar Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="13634770000t" end="13656850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">Kau pilih untuk tidak mendewakan aku!</p>
<p begin="13663930000t" end="13685180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">Tapi aku masih beri peluang kepada kau.</p>
<p begin="13703930000t" end="13731430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">Pintu kemaafan aku masih terbuka<br/>untuk kau.</p>
<p begin="13753100000t" end="13763100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">Mak!</p>
<p begin="13767680000t" end="13779350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">Lepaskan aku!</p>
<p begin="13816020000t" end="13826020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">Diam!</p>
<p begin="13906020000t" end="13916020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">Diam!</p>
<p begin="13948100000t" end="13959350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">Aina!</p>
<p begin="13981850000t" end="13994350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">Duduklah, Adam.</p>
<p begin="14001020000t" end="14042680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">Sebelum Adam datang tadi,<br/>Mak sempat masak lauk kegemaran Adam.</p>
<p begin="14048520000t" end="14061020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">Adam minta maaf, Mak.</p>
<p begin="14071850000t" end="14088520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">Adam bukan nak sakitkan hati Mak.</p>
<p begin="14089770000t" end="14119770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">Selama ni Adam berjihad<br/>untuk tentang nafsu Adam sendiri.</p>
<p begin="14121020000t" end="14147680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">Nafsu untuk henti tolong orang,<br/>henti ruqyahkan orang.</p>
<p begin="14149350000t" end="14165600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">Nafsu untuk berhenti berdakwah.</p>
<p begin="14171850000t" end="14186430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">Adam cuba untuk istiqamah.</p>
<p begin="14187680000t" end="14200180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">Mak tahu</p>
<p begin="14203100000t" end="14228930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">Adam berusaha mencari hidayah Allah</p>
<p begin="14229770000t" end="14251020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">samalah macam Mak, Adam.</p>
<p begin="14254770000t" end="14294770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">Untuk mencari hidayah,<br/>kadang-kadang Mak keliru.</p>
<p begin="14298100000t" end="14322270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">terutama di zaman fitnah ini.</p>
<p begin="14324770000t" end="14347270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">Mak risaukan keselamatan Adam.</p>
<p begin="14352270000t" end="14372270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">Mak tak sanggup kehilangan kau, nak.</p>
<p begin="14374770000t" end="14385600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">Demi Tuhan, Mak</p>
<p begin="14396430000t" end="14417680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">Kelebihan yang Allah berikan<br/>kepada Adam ni</p>
<p begin="14421850000t" end="14451430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">akan dipertanggungjawabkan<br/>di akhirat nanti.</p>
<p begin="14456850000t" end="14472680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">Adam tak boleh nak sia-siakan.</p>
<p begin="14474770000t" end="14507690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">Adam cuma minta satu sahaja;<br/>setiap langkah Adam, Mak doakan.</p>
<p begin="14521020000t" end="14531020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">Tolonglah Mak.</p>
<p begin="14535180000t" end="14546850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">Iizinkan Adam pergi.</p>
<p begin="14570600000t" end="14580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">Macam mana Adam?</p>
<p begin="14583520000t" end="14609350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">Kalau nak pergi,<br/>kita perlu bergerak sekarang</p>
<p begin="14611430000t" end="14622270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">sebelum hari gelap.</p>
<p begin="14625600000t" end="14634770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">Adam.</p>
<p begin="14637680000t" end="14668100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">Kerana Allah, Mak izinkan Adam pergi.</p>
<p begin="14678100000t" end="14724350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">Apa jadi sekali pun,<br/>Mak nak Adam balik malam ini juga.</p>
<p begin="14747270000t" end="14759350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">Insya Allah, Mak.</p>
<p begin="14801850000t" end="14858520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">Ajaran sesat yang Abuja sebarkan ni memang<br/>bertentangan dengan al-Quran dan Sunnah.</p>
<p begin="14859350000t" end="14898930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">Pengikut Abuja pula percaya<br/>kononnya Abuja ni manusia mulia</p>
<p begin="14901430000t" end="14928520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">dan selalu terima ilham<br/>dari langit dan mimpi.</p>
<p begin="14933520000t" end="14952270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">Ilham apa pula ni, Azhar?</p>
<p begin="14953100000t" end="14985600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">Abuja ni mesti<br/>golongan anti hadis Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="14986850000t" end="15011020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">Tapi takkan semudah tu<br/>orang kampung terpengaruh?</p>
<p begin="15013100000t" end="15036850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">Takkan tiada sesiapa<br/>yang berani menentang dia?</p>
<p begin="15038930000t" end="15068510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">Bapa Sakinah orang<br/>yang paling kuat tentang Abuja dulu.</p>
<p begin="15070180000t" end="15094760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">Sebab itu Imam Malik sakit<br/>sampai hari ini.</p>
<p begin="15096430000t" end="15115600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">Yang jadi mangsa sekarang, Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="15116430000t" end="15131010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">Dia bukan saja guna kekerasan</p>
<p begin="15132680000t" end="15169350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">tapi dia akan guna sihir<br/>untuk hukum orang yang tentang ajarannya.</p>
<p begin="15170180000t" end="15184770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">Jadi orang kampung kau takut?</p>
<p begin="15189350000t" end="15209350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">Tak berani lapor pada pihak berkuasa?</p>
<p begin="15210600000t" end="15223520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">Takkan sampai macam itu?</p>
<p begin="15224350000t" end="15238100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">Ada yang mati kena bunuh.</p>
<p begin="15476850000t" end="15488930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">Assalamualaikum!</p>
<p begin="15504770000t" end="15514770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">Sakinah!</p>
