<p begin="15561020000t" end="15571020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="15596850000t" end="15611020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">Tak ada siapa di rumah ke?</p>
<p begin="15624350000t" end="15634350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">Ada.</p>
<p begin="15640600000t" end="15650600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">Banyak.</p>
<p begin="15663100000t" end="15673520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">Aku rasa macam ni.</p>
<p begin="15677270000t" end="15691430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">Biar aku seorang masuk dulu.</p>
<p begin="15692270000t" end="15706020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">Kamu berdua tunggu di luar.</p>
<p begin="15711430000t" end="15727260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">Lidah jangan berhenti berzikir.</p>
<p begin="15733100000t" end="15747270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">Kita masuk sekalilah Adam?</p>
<p begin="15753100000t" end="15766430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">Kan aku selalu teman kau?</p>
<p begin="15777680000t" end="15787680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">Kenapa ini?</p>
<p begin="15797680000t" end="15827680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">Kalau ada apa-apa, aku dan Azhar boleh...</p>
<p begin="15841430000t" end="15850600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">Adam!</p>
