<p begin="16245180000t" end="16271020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">Apa yang ada dalam bilik itu<br/>bukan Ayah saya, Ustaz.</p>
<p begin="16276850000t" end="16287680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">Itu bukan dia.</p>
<p begin="16293520000t" end="16310180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">Selamatkan dia, Ustaz.</p>
<p begin="16315600000t" end="16326430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">Tolong saya.</p>
<p begin="16331430000t" end="16352270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">Saya tak nak Ayah saya mati.</p>
<p begin="16617270000t" end="16645600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">Dengan nama Allah<br/>yang Maha Pemurah lagi Maha Mengasihani</p>
<p begin="16646430000t" end="16706850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al Baqarah, Ayat 148</span></p>
<p begin="16708520000t" end="16719350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">Jangan kacau aku!</p>
