<p begin="18381430000t" end="18407680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">Aku berlindung dengan kalimah-kalimahMu<br/>ya Allah!</p>
<p begin="18422680000t" end="18441020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">Bismillahirrahmanirrahim.</p>
<p begin="18443930000t" end="18513930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al A'raf, Ayat 117-123</span></p>
<p begin="18742270000t" end="18763930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">Subhanallah!</p>
<p begin="18869770000t" end="18878100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">Imam.</p>
<p begin="18883930000t" end="18893930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">Imam.</p>
<p begin="19014770000t" end="19041430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">Daripada Allah kita datang,<br/>kepada Allah kita kembali.</p>
<p begin="19196430000t" end="19208520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="19273520000t" end="19302690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">Tiada daya dan kekuatan<br/>melainkan dengan pertolongan Allah.</p>
<p begin="19303520000t" end="19361440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">Kerajaan Firaun yang kuat<br/>juga meminta pertolongan iblis.</p>
<p begin="19385600000t" end="19411430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">Muslim munafik dan kafir.</p>
<p begin="19412270000t" end="19435600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">Akan ku pecah belahkan semuanya!</p>
<p begin="19438930000t" end="19479770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">-Berperanglah kamu semua!<br/>-Aku hanya takutkan Allah, bukan syaitan.</p>
<p begin="19486020000t" end="19519770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">Iblis akan bunuh dan hancurkan kau.</p>
<p begin="19520600000t" end="19544350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">Jangan kau Islamkan aku!</p>
<p begin="19553930000t" end="19563930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">Mataku sakit, Azhar!</p>
<p begin="19573930000t" end="19594770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">Mataku panas, Azhar! Mataku panas!</p>
<p begin="19595600000t" end="19653520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al Israa', Ayat 82</span></p>
<p begin="19655180000t" end="19696020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">Ketua aku akan marah pada aku.<br/>Iblislah ketua aku!</p>
<p begin="19697270000t" end="19709350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">Allah Maha Besar!</p>
<p begin="19710600000t" end="19729770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">Iblislah ketua aku!</p>
<p begin="19761250000t" end="19777920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">Aku jin Satan!</p>
<p begin="19781250000t" end="19798330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">Syaitan Satan!</p>
<p begin="19800180000t" end="19813520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">Tunggu ya iblis...</p>
<p begin="19814350000t" end="19847270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">Paling kuat antara semua jin!</p>
<p begin="19854350000t" end="19883930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">azab yang pedih di akhirat.</p>
<p begin="19885180000t" end="19924350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><span style="s1_1">Surat Asy-syu'araa', Ayat 80</span></p>
<p begin="19925180000t" end="19954770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">Allah Maha Besar!</p>
<p begin="20249350000t" end="20259350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">Sakinah mana?</p>
<p begin="20261020000t" end="20271020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">Sakinah dah lari.</p>
