<p begin="20346850000t" end="20358520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">Allah Maha Besar!</p>
<p begin="20456020000t" end="20464350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="20465180000t" end="20473520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="20490600000t" end="20500600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">Sakinah!</p>
<p begin="20518100000t" end="20532270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">Semoga Allah mengampuniku.</p>
<p begin="20565180000t" end="20628100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">Rasulullah berkata,<br/>Dajjal akan muncul di kalangan umatnya.</p>
<p begin="20628930000t" end="20649770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">Dia bermata satu!</p>
<p begin="20650600000t" end="20671430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">Aku mohon kepada Allah<br/>tak bertemu Dajjal!</p>
<p begin="20672270000t" end="20723520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">Fitnah Dajjal<br/>adalah ujian terbesar umat Islam.</p>
<p begin="20724350000t" end="20762270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">Walau Dajjal mengaku sebagai Tuhan,<br/>orang Islam takkan percaya dan akuinya!</p>
<p begin="20763100000t" end="20786430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">kerana Tauhid dan Iman kepada Allah.</p>
<p begin="20787270000t" end="20833520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">Selama 40 hari Dajjal<br/>akan menghasut anak Adam nanti!</p>
<p begin="20846020000t" end="20885600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">Bagaimana kamu solat nanti?<br/>Ramai yang akan tinggalkan Islam.</p>
<p begin="20886430000t" end="20928520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">Selagi manusia beriman kepada Allah,<br/>kiamat tidak akan berlaku!</p>
<p begin="20929350000t" end="20992270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">Kita semua berada di akhir zaman.<br/>Kiamat sudah dekat!</p>
<p begin="21017270000t" end="21087270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414"><span style="s1_1">Surat Taha, Ayat 68-70</span></p>
<p begin="21190180000t" end="21240180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">Aku tak akan mati sehingga hari kiamat!</p>
<p begin="21256850000t" end="21279770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">Keluarlah kau iblis!</p>
<p begin="21306850000t" end="21376850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">Surat Yunus, Ayat 81-84</p>
<p begin="21462680000t" end="21501020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">Sesat dan kafirlah kamu sekalian mukmin!</p>
<p begin="21515600000t" end="21573100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">Ya'juj Ma'juj</p>
<p begin="21581850000t" end="21621020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">Kamilah umat Rasulullah SAW!</p>
<p begin="21621850000t" end="21659770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">Aku tidak akan kalah!</p>
<p begin="21666850000t" end="21703520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">Allah melaknat engkau iblis,<br/>sehingga hari kiamat!</p>
<p begin="21967680000t" end="21976020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="22528100000t" end="22548930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">Kenapa kau datang?</p>
<p begin="22561850000t" end="22582680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">Adam!</p>
<p begin="22600180000t" end="22623930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">Ayah kau sebenarnya dah lama meninggal,<br/>Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="22643930000t" end="22683510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">Ada jin yang dihantar untuk duduk<br/>dalam badan Ayah kau selama ini.</p>
<p begin="22684350000t" end="22729350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">Walaupun manusia dah ada roh, tapi jin<br/>syaitan boleh masuk ikut saluran darah.</p>
<p begin="22730180000t" end="22761430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">Majoriti ahli sunnah setuju jin<br/>boleh merasuk manusia.</p>
<p begin="22762270000t" end="22784350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">Tak perlu Ustaz beritahu saya<br/>angkara siapa.</p>
<p begin="22787270000t" end="22809770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">Ini semua perbuatan manusia yang murtad</p>
<p begin="22817270000t" end="22831020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">kejam seperti Abuja.</p>
<p begin="22843520000t" end="22873940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">Saya akan menuntut bela<br/>kematian Ayah saya.</p>
<p begin="22888100000t" end="22906850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">Abuja akan dapat balasan dia.</p>
<p begin="22908930000t" end="22933100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">Fikir dulu sebelum bertindak apa-apa,<br/>Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="22941850000t" end="22973930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">Kau kena ingat, kita ada agama,<br/>ada pegangan.</p>
<p begin="22977270000t" end="23009770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">Adam, macam mana dengan arwah ini?<br/>Siapa nak uruskan?</p>
<p begin="23010600000t" end="23020600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">Tak apa.</p>
<p begin="23021430000t" end="23049770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">Aku akan uruskan jenazah ini<br/>dengan kawan-kawan aku.</p>
<p begin="23053100000t" end="23070600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">Insya Allah, Abuja takkan tahu.</p>
<p begin="23071430000t" end="23086850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">Apa yang dah berlaku...</p>
<p begin="23103520000t" end="23123520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">menguji keimanan saya, Ustaz.</p>
<p begin="23124350000t" end="23157680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">Saya tak tahu sejauh mana lagi<br/>saya boleh bertahan.</p>
<p begin="23160180000t" end="23190180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">-Di mana Allah bila saya perlukan Dia?<br/>-Istighfar, Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="23191020000t" end="23235600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">Bukan semua perkara yang Allah izin,<br/>Allah redha. Solat, sujud, tahajjud, doa.</p>
