<p begin="23568100000t" end="23587680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">Biasa je orangnya.</p>
<p begin="23588930000t" end="23603930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">Tak pakai serban</p>
<p begin="23607270000t" end="23634350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">tapi mengaku ikut sunnah Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="23638100000t" end="23661430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">Setahu aku, yang namanya Ustaz</p>
<p begin="23662270000t" end="23686850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">akan bermati-matian<br/>mengikut telunjuk Nabi.</p>
<p begin="23688100000t" end="23711430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">Ahli sunnah wal jamaah jenis apa kau ini?</p>
<p begin="23713520000t" end="23740190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">Jangan menilai orang<br/>dengan hanya tengok pada luaran.</p>
<p begin="23741020000t" end="23786850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">Berpakaian, serban bkn sunnah dituntut dlm<br/>agama. Ia termasuk dlm sunnah Jibiliah.</p>
<p begin="23787680000t" end="23812270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">Kita disuruh untuk membaca semua kitab</p>
<p begin="23813100000t" end="23855600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">Bukan baca satu dua kitab, lepas itu<br/>memandai-mandai buat kesimpulan sendiri.</p>
<p begin="23858520000t" end="23877680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">Malu bertanya, sesat jalan.</p>
