<p begin="40352680000t" end="40363520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle744">Terutamanya Abuja!</p>
<p begin="40365180000t" end="40394760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle745">Memanglah dia tak maksum,<br/>tapi ilmunya tinggi daripada kau!</p>
<p begin="40401020000t" end="40429770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle746">Ustaz, makam Abuja<br/>lebih tinggi dari Ustaz!</p>
<p begin="40430600000t" end="40444770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle747">Ustaz siapa nak lawan dia!</p>
<p begin="40445600000t" end="40453930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle748">Betul tak?</p>
<p begin="40454770000t" end="40469770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle749">Ya, betul itu.</p>
<p begin="40483520000t" end="40512270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle750">Saidina Umar,<br/>sahabat Nabi sendiri pernah mengatakan:</p>
<p begin="40513930000t" end="40542270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle751">Jika engkau tengok aku menyeleweng,<br/>perbetulkan aku.</p>
<p begin="40543100000t" end="40587270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle752">Itu kata Saidina Omar al-Khattab!<br/>Inikan Abuja yang jelas kekufurannya!</p>
<p begin="40588100000t" end="40598520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle753">Kita bukan jahiliah!</p>
<p begin="40625600000t" end="40635600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle754">Abuja.</p>
<p begin="40645600000t" end="40675600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle755">Orang kita beritahu,<br/>Adam ada di kampung kita sekarang ini.</p>
<p begin="40677680000t" end="40688520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle756">Dia datang berdakwah.</p>
<p begin="40689350000t" end="40702270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle757">Pada masa yang sama,</p>
<p begin="40705600000t" end="40743100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle758">dia buruk-burukkan<br/>dan maki hamun kau depan orang kampung!</p>
<p begin="40743930000t" end="40768520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle759">Ada yang mula termakan kata-kata dia.</p>
<p begin="40773100000t" end="40795180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle760">Kalau rahsia kita bocor, macam mana?</p>
<p begin="40796430000t" end="40820600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle761">Ramai yang akan berpaling dari kau, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="40826850000t" end="40843930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle762">Allah telah mengutuskan Rasul</p>
<p begin="40853100000t" end="40872270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle763">bukan hanya untuk kebaikan orang Arab,</p>
<p begin="40873100000t" end="40902270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle764">orang Melayu dan orang Islam sahaja,<br/>tapi sekalian alam!</p>
<p begin="40903100000t" end="40948100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle765">Nabi Muhammad SAW,<br/>dialah Rasul yang dihantar oleh Allah.</p>
<p begin="40951430000t" end="40970180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle766">Sesiapa yang menjadi hamba manusia,</p>
<p begin="40974350000t" end="40995180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle767">tidak akan jadi hamba Allah yang sebenar.</p>
<p begin="40999770000t" end="41023100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle768">Islam datang untuk memerdekakan jiwa kita.</p>
<p begin="41024350000t" end="41053930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle769">Kita mesti jadi umat Islam yang hidup,<br/>dan yang membangun.</p>
<p begin="41054770000t" end="41080180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle770">Buang segala perkara syirik<br/>dan karut dari Abuja.</p>
<p begin="41081020000t" end="41096430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle771">Kita hanya berTuhankan Allah.</p>
<p begin="41098100000t" end="41108100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle772">Ya, betul. Betul.</p>
<p begin="41108930000t" end="41119770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle773">Allah semata-mata.</p>
<p begin="41124770000t" end="41162680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle774">Siapa kau nak bercakap tentang dalil,<br/>pasal agama?</p>
<p begin="41164350000t" end="41192270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle775">Kau patut hormat, melutut depan aku.<br/>Aku lebih tua.</p>
<p begin="41206430000t" end="41226020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle776">Dah berapa banyak hadis yang kau hafal?</p>
<p begin="41226850000t" end="41242680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle777">Seribu? Dua ribu?</p>
<p begin="41244350000t" end="41277270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle778">Hadis Imam Bukhari kau belum khatam.<br/>Jangan tunjuk pandai di sini.</p>
<p begin="41278100000t" end="41320180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle779">Semua orang yang ada dekat sini tahu,<br/>aku lebih faham al-Quran dari kau.</p>
<p begin="41321020000t" end="41356430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle780">Yang lebih faham al-Quran adalah<br/>As-salafussoleh, sahabat Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="41357270000t" end="41371850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle781">Tabi'in, athbau tabi'in.</p>
<p begin="41372680000t" end="41384770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle782">Bukan kau, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="41385600000t" end="41427680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle783">Jika kau beriman seperti Nabi dan<br/>para sahabat, kau berada di atas petunjuk.</p>
<p begin="41430600000t" end="41455600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle784">Jika kau berpaling,<br/>jelas kau dalam kesesatan.</p>
<p begin="41456430000t" end="41494770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle785">Nampaknya kau masih belum serik,<br/>belum puas dengan musibah.</p>
<p begin="41506020000t" end="41520190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle786">Kau nak malukan aku?</p>
<p begin="41521020000t" end="41545600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle787">Kau takkan terlepas, Abuja.<br/>Masa kau dah sampai.</p>
<p begin="41546430000t" end="41566430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle788">Aku akan laporkan kepada pihak berkuasa.</p>
<p begin="41570600000t" end="41598100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle789">Aku tahu, kau yang bunuh Mak aku.</p>
<p begin="41601020000t" end="41617270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle790">Apa, kau tak takut pada mati?</p>
<p begin="41635600000t" end="41666850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle791">Tak ada manusia yang tak takut<br/>pada kematian. Termasuk kau!</p>
<p begin="41696020000t" end="41716850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle792">Aku sanggup mati untuk perjuangkan Islam.</p>
<p begin="41717680000t" end="41753930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle793">Hati dan jiwa kau dah lama mati<br/>sebelum kematian kau yang sebenar, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="41754770000t" end="41773520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle794">Kau cinta dunia dan takut kematian.</p>
<p begin="41774350000t" end="41799770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle795">Cintakan dunia tapi benci pada kematian!</p>
<p begin="42019350000t" end="42040180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle796">Selama ni aku berdosa ke, Adam?</p>
<p begin="42041020000t" end="42051020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle797">Sebab...</p>
<p begin="42059350000t" end="42101850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle798">Aku tahu yang ajaran Abuja ni sesat,<br/>tapi aku diamkan diri.</p>
<p begin="42128930000t" end="42159770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle799">Aku tak berani<br/>nak pertahankan agama aku sendiri.</p>
<p begin="42175180000t" end="42195180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle800">Aku bukan pentingkan diri, Adam.</p>
<p begin="42200180000t" end="42208520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle801">Tapi...</p>
<p begin="42209350000t" end="42255600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle802">Cukup kau tolak ajarannya dengan hati kau,<br/>Azhar. Sebab aku tahu kau tak mampu.</p>
<p begin="42259770000t" end="42271440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle803">Tak apa, Azhar.</p>
<p begin="42272680000t" end="42299350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle804">Keikhlasan kita yang akan dinilai<br/>di sisi Allah nanti.</p>
<p begin="42307680000t" end="42368930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle805">Menentang kemungkaran hanya dengan hati,<br/>itu selemah-lemah iman, Adam.</p>
<p begin="42369770000t" end="42403100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle806">Menolak, menentang kemungkaran itu<br/>memang wajib atas setiap Muslim.</p>
<p begin="42406020000t" end="42430190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle807">Tapi ikut kemampuan, dan kekuatan kau.</p>
<p begin="42439770000t" end="42448930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle808">Sabar, Azhar.</p>
<p begin="42471850000t" end="42490180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle809">Dulu aku ada isteri, Adam.</p>
<p begin="42511430000t" end="42555600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle810">Tapi isteri aku derhaka sebab terpengaruh<br/>dengan ajaran Abuja, Adam.</p>
<p begin="42560600000t" end="42576430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle811">Disebabkan terlalu taksub,</p>
<p begin="42591850000t" end="42610180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle812">dia tinggalkan aku seorang-seorang.</p>
<p begin="42626850000t" end="42644350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle813">Hidayah itu memang milik Allah...</p>
<p begin="42655600000t" end="42683930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle814">dan tak semua orang dapat.</p>
<p begin="42694350000t" end="42711850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle815">Sebab itu sampai hari ini,</p>
<p begin="42725600000t" end="42743520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle816">aku berdoa, Adam, hari-hari...</p>
<p begin="42757270000t" end="42808100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle817">supaya isteri aku kembali pada Islam.</p>
<p begin="42815180000t" end="42846010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle818">Dalam perjuangan Islam ini,<br/>tak semuanya indah, Azhar.</p>
<p begin="42855180000t" end="42874770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle819">Tak semuanya indah.</p>
<p begin="42896430000t" end="42906020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle820">Adam!</p>
<p begin="42912270000t" end="42920600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle821">Pergi, Azhar!</p>
<p begin="42923100000t" end="42933100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle822">Pergi, aku cakap!</p>
<p begin="42938520000t" end="42956020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle823">Kau pelampau agama, Adam!</p>
<p begin="42956850000t" end="42981020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle824">Jangan ingat semua telan<br/>bulat2 apa yg kau cakap!</p>
<p begin="42981850000t" end="43008520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle825">Kau lah penyebab perpecahan<br/>di dalam kampung ni.</p>
<p begin="43009350000t" end="43045600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle826">Akidah siapa yang sesat sekarang?<br/>Aku tanya kau, akidah siapa yang sesat?</p>
<p begin="43046430000t" end="43075600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle827">Allah ampunkan kekufuran<br/>disebabkan kejahilan.</p>
<p begin="43076430000t" end="43093930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle828">Aku sayangkan kamu semua, tahu tak?</p>
<p begin="43095180000t" end="43103520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle829">Bertaubatlah!</p>
<p begin="43105180000t" end="43142270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle830">Hujah kau amat halus, Adam. Tapi jahat.</p>
<p begin="43144770000t" end="43173520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle831">Ilmu agama kau cetek. Kalam kau lemah.</p>
<p begin="43174350000t" end="43201020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle832">Ahlus-Sunnah wal-Jama'ah sepatutnya<br/>buat kita insaf,</p>
<p begin="43201850000t" end="43235180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle833">bukan sesat dan kafirkan orang<br/>yang berbeza ijtihad dan pandangan.</p>
<p begin="43236020000t" end="43260180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle834">Kita tak boleh nak tunjuk pandai<br/>melebihi Tuhan.</p>
<p begin="43261020000t" end="43271850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle835">Takkan kamu tak tahu?</p>
<p begin="43333100000t" end="43378520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle836">Sepatutnya masa polis datang semalam,<br/>aku kena maklumkan juga pasal Abuja.</p>
<p begin="43381020000t" end="43426020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle837">Sebab mungkin orang-orang dia<br/>yang bunuh isteri aku.</p>
<p begin="43426850000t" end="43449350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle838">Kita tak ada bukti Abuja yang buat.</p>
<p begin="43452270000t" end="43475600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle839">Kita tak boleh serkap jarang, Pak Rahim.</p>
<p begin="43478930000t" end="43534770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle840">Sekurang-kurangnya, polis tangkap dia<br/>sebab ajaran sesat yang dia bawa.</p>
<p begin="43536020000t" end="43571430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle841">Kalau bukan kita,<br/>siapa lagi yang berani buat laporan?</p>
<p begin="43573930000t" end="43596430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle842">Habis itu, keselamatan kita ni macam mana?</p>
<p begin="43600180000t" end="43634760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle843">Pak Rahim, Pak Rahim tahu tak<br/>Abuja itu sanggup bunuh orang?</p>
<p begin="43636430000t" end="43653930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle844">Apa pun, kita tunggu Adam.</p>
<p begin="43667680000t" end="43676020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle845">Pak Rahim!</p>
<p begin="43681430000t" end="43689770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle846">Azhar.</p>
<p begin="43696430000t" end="43708930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle847">Apahal ini, Azhar?</p>
<p begin="43714770000t" end="43723100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle848">Adam mana?</p>
<p begin="43725180000t" end="43751010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle849">Pengikut Abuja dah tangkap Adam,<br/>Pak Rahim!</p>
<p begin="43751850000t" end="43764770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle850">Adam dalam bahaya ini!</p>
<p begin="43767270000t" end="43775600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle851">Ya Allah!</p>
<p begin="43776430000t" end="43820180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle852">-Semoga Allah mengampuniku.<br/>-Cepat, Man, pergi report polis. Sekarang!</p>
<p begin="43821020000t" end="43841020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle853">-Pergi, Man!<br/>-Baik, baik, baik Pak Rahim.</p>
<p begin="43859350000t" end="43875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle854">Saya sempat ikut mereka tadi.</p>
<p begin="43876430000t" end="43900600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle855">Mereka bawa Adam pergi<br/>ke satu rumah usang.</p>
<p begin="43903100000t" end="43933100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle856">Saya rasa Abuja takkan lepaskan Adam<br/>kali ini.</p>
<p begin="43935180000t" end="43945180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle857">Allah...</p>
<p begin="44213520000t" end="44223520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle858">Ya Allah.</p>
<p begin="44234770000t" end="44244770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle859">Omar!</p>
<p begin="44272270000t" end="44282270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle860">Omar!</p>
<p begin="44823100000t" end="44893100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle861"><span style="s1_1">Ayat Al-Kursi</span></p>
<p begin="45061850000t" end="45082680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle862">Allah Maha Besar!</p>
<p begin="45498520000t" end="45508520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle863">Ya Allah.</p>
<p begin="45812680000t" end="45826850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle864">Kau kafir!</p>
<p begin="45888100000t" end="45898930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle865">Ya Allah.</p>
<p begin="46186850000t" end="46218520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle866">Abuja, aku dah hantar Adam<br/>ke tempat yang kau suruh.</p>
<p begin="46220180000t" end="46241020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle867">Kenapa tak arahkan bunuh sahaja dia?</p>
<p begin="46242270000t" end="46266850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle868">Kematian sahaja tak cukup untuk dia.</p>
<p begin="46267680000t" end="46318520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle869">Dia perlu tahu dan rasakan betapa besarnya<br/>kuasa sihir dan kekuatan aku.</p>
<p begin="46319350000t" end="46328520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle870">Ustaz Adam...</p>
<p begin="46341850000t" end="46359350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle871">Apa yang kau nak buat dengan dia?</p>
<p begin="46360180000t" end="46384770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle872">Kalau kau tak nak tengok anak kau mati,</p>
<p begin="46385600000t" end="46444350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle873">dan kau nak aku lepaskan kau dan anak kau,<br/>kau perlu buat sesuatu untuk aku.</p>
<p begin="46447680000t" end="46466850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle874">Demi anak kesayangan kau.</p>
<p begin="46592270000t" end="46603520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle875">Baik-baik, Pak Rahim</p>
<p begin="46879350000t" end="46898520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle876">Kau cari Adam di bilik depan itu.</p>
<p begin="46949350000t" end="46958520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle877">Pak Rahim!</p>
<p begin="46964770000t" end="46976430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle878">-Pak Rahim!<br/>-Ya.</p>
<p begin="47011430000t" end="47021430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle879">Adam...</p>
<p begin="47051020000t" end="47061020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle880">Adam!</p>
<p begin="47568520000t" end="47585180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle881">Ya Allah, Adam!</p>
<p begin="47602680000t" end="47613520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle882">Azhar!</p>
<p begin="47708930000t" end="47745180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle883">Ada yang munafik di kalangan kamu.<br/>Tanpa kau sedar.</p>
<p begin="47746020000t" end="47791850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle884">Aku berlindung kepada Allah<br/>dari syaitan yang direjam.</p>
<p begin="47792680000t" end="47822270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle885">Bismillahirrahmanirrahim.</p>
<p begin="47858100000t" end="47924770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle886"><span style="s1_1">Surat Al-Hasyr, Ayat 21</span></p>
<p begin="47992680000t" end="48062680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle887"><span style="s1_1">Hadith Abu Dawud dan At-Tirmidhi</span></p>
<p begin="48196850000t" end="48228930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle888">Lakhnat Allah dan Rasulnya<br/>hingga ke hari akhirat.</p>
<p begin="48229770000t" end="48266440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle889">Ya Allah, limpahkanlah kesejahteraan<br/>kepada Nabi Muhammad.</p>
<p begin="48268930000t" end="48290180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle890">Selawat keatas junjungan besar Muhammad.</p>
<p begin="48291020000t" end="48310600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle891">Selawat sebanyak ilmu<br/>pengetahuan Allah.</p>
<p begin="48311430000t" end="48331010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle892">Akan aku pecah belahkan semua Muslim!</p>
<p begin="48336020000t" end="48356020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle893">Beperanglah kamu semua!</p>
<p begin="48356850000t" end="48408100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle894">Selawat yang berkekalan<br/>selama kekalnya kekuasaan Allah.</p>
<p begin="48467270000t" end="48491850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle895">Adam! Ya Allah ya Tuhanku. Adam!</p>
<p begin="48493100000t" end="48504350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle896">Adam!</p>
<p begin="48505180000t" end="48513520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle897">Adam!</p>
<p begin="48592680000t" end="48623930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle898">Dengan menyebut nama Tuhan,<br/>aku bertawakkal kepadaNya.</p>
<p begin="48674350000t" end="48715180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle899">Anak kau dah mati,<br/>ilmu Al Qur'an dia masih cetek.</p>
<p begin="48716430000t" end="48740600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle900">Dia bukan umat Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="48764770000t" end="48780600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle901">Ingat Allah, Adam!</p>
<p begin="48785600000t" end="48807270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle902">Cuba lawan bisikan syaitan!</p>
<p begin="48824350000t" end="48857270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle903">Dengan izin Engkau padaku<br/>Aku pagar diri aku dan ruhku</p>
<p begin="48858100000t" end="48890600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle904">Dengan nama Allah Jibril dikananku.</p>
<p begin="48892270000t" end="48926850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle905">Dengan nama Allah Mikail dikiriku.</p>
<p begin="48930180000t" end="48967270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle906">Dengan nama Allah Israfil dihadapan ku.</p>
<p begin="48971430000t" end="49012680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle907">Dengan nama Allah Izrail dibelakang ku.</p>
<p begin="49026850000t" end="49057270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle908">Kamu semua sudah terkena belitan iblis!</p>
<p begin="49081430000t" end="49121430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle909">Tuhanmu Wahai Rasulullah<br/>Kembalilah kepada Allah</p>
<p begin="49122270000t" end="49162270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle910">Bantulah Aku Wahai Rasulullah</p>
<p begin="49163520000t" end="49217270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle911">Tiada tuhan melainkan Allah<br/>Muhammad Rasulullah.</p>
<p begin="49407680000t" end="49416020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle912">Ayah.</p>
<p begin="49443930000t" end="49452270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle913">Adam.</p>
<p begin="49493520000t" end="49543100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle914">Azhar, sebelum jadi apa-apa,<br/>baik minta tolong dengan kawan-kawan kau.</p>
<p begin="49543930000t" end="49566850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle915">Suruh mereka semua datang sini.</p>
<p begin="49570180000t" end="49581850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle916">Cepat, Azhar.</p>
<p begin="49587680000t" end="49597680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle917">Cepat.</p>
<p begin="49753100000t" end="49763100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle918">Azhar!</p>
<p begin="49965600000t" end="49978930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle919">Abuja!</p>
<p begin="50004350000t" end="50016020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle920">Allah!</p>
<p begin="50043100000t" end="50070600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle921">Inilah contoh manusia akhir zaman.</p>
<p begin="50071430000t" end="50088100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle922">Golongan pendusta!</p>
<p begin="50088930000t" end="50121850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle923">Tetapi membawa hadis, bertopengkan agama.</p>
<p begin="50122680000t" end="50144770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle924">Sedangkan dia sebenarnya pendakwah palsu.</p>
<p begin="50146430000t" end="50176010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle925">Menyeru manusia masuk<br/>ke dalam neraka Hawiyah.</p>
<p begin="50188520000t" end="50235600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle926">Sakinah, beritahu semua orang kampung ini,<br/>apa yang Ustaz Adam dah buat pada kau.</p>
<p begin="50239770000t" end="50250600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle927">Cakap, Sakinah.</p>
<p begin="50252680000t" end="50292680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle928">Abuja nak kau beritahu semua orang<br/>apa yang Adam ni dah buat pada kau. Cakap!</p>
<p begin="50296850000t" end="50310180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle929">Dia manusia...</p>
<p begin="50314770000t" end="50340600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle930">suka ambil kesempatan atas nama agama.</p>
<p begin="50345180000t" end="50366430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle931">Dia buat banyak kerosakan pada perempuan.</p>
<p begin="50367270000t" end="50394770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle932">Ustaz Adam rogol aku depan anak aku.</p>
<p begin="50403100000t" end="50418930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle933">Ha? Rogol?</p>
<p begin="50425600000t" end="50446850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle934">Rogol? Ye ke? Betul ke ini?</p>
<p begin="50447680000t" end="50457680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle935">Kenapa, Sakinah?</p>
<p begin="50477270000t" end="50494350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle936">Kenapa fitnah aku?</p>
<p begin="50508100000t" end="50524350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle937">Apa yang dia cakap semua fitnah!</p>
<p begin="50537270000t" end="50546850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle938">Semuanya fitnah!</p>
<p begin="50549350000t" end="50574770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle939">Dia ini kaki maksiat! Golongan fasik!</p>
<p begin="50575600000t" end="50606430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle940">Kamu perlu hati-hati<br/>dengan golongan Ustaz yang macam ini.</p>
<p begin="50609350000t" end="50628520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle941">Dia bagi bala bencana pada kita!</p>
<p begin="50629350000t" end="50658520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle942">Nanti dulu.<br/>Kita semua tak boleh percaya macam ini.</p>
<p begin="50659350000t" end="50674770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle943">Jangan-jangan ini fitnah!</p>
<p begin="50675600000t" end="50706020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle944">Abuja! Apa-apa pun,<br/>kita kena ada bukti dulu.</p>
<p begin="50726020000t" end="50736020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle945">Aku buktinya.</p>
<p begin="50879770000t" end="50911850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle946">Memang dia yang rogol Sakinah.<br/>Bukan Sakinah sahaja yang dirogol.</p>
<p begin="50912680000t" end="50955180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle947">Ramai yang jadi mangsa dia. Lebih sepuluh<br/>tahun aku berkawan baik dengan dia.</p>
<p begin="50956020000t" end="50973100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle948">Aku lebih kenal dia daripada kamu.</p>
<p begin="50977680000t" end="51026430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle949">Selama ini, aku seorang saja yang tahu<br/>baik dan buruk perangai Ustaz ini.</p>
<p begin="51033100000t" end="51054770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle950">Tak sanggup lagi<br/>aku nak tutup aib dia lagi.</p>
<p begin="51055600000t" end="51063930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle951">Azman!</p>
<p begin="51066430000t" end="51087270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle952">Kenapa kau fitnah Adam?</p>
<p begin="51099770000t" end="51113100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle953">Mana iman kamu?</p>
<p begin="51118100000t" end="51145600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle954">Syaitan mana yang telah merasuk kamu ini?</p>
<p begin="51156430000t" end="51183100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle955">Kamu semua jangan percaya!</p>
<p begin="51581430000t" end="51591430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle956">Adam.</p>
<p begin="51607680000t" end="51632680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle957">Banyak benda yang kau tak tahu lagi, Adam.</p>
<p begin="51633520000t" end="51657270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle958">Dan malam ini semuanya akan terjawab.</p>
<p begin="51671850000t" end="51694770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle959">Aku yang bunuh Maria dulu, Adam.</p>
<p begin="51703100000t" end="51713100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle960">Aku!</p>
<p begin="51726850000t" end="51736850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle961">Aku, Adam.</p>
<p begin="51741430000t" end="51769760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle962">Dah lama aku tahu kau yang tolak Maria,<br/>Azman.</p>
<p begin="51773100000t" end="51801430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle963">Sebenarnya kau lah orang<br/>yang selalu ada dalam mimpi aku.</p>
<p begin="51806430000t" end="51856430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle964">Segala mimpi tu<br/>rupanya petanda dari Tuhan.</p>
<p begin="51860600000t" end="51874770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle965">Aku terpaksa, Adam.</p>
<p begin="51878930000t" end="51916430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle966">Aku takut Maria akan membongkar hubunganku<br/>dengan ayahnya.</p>
<p begin="51917680000t" end="51954770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle967">Aku terpaksa bunuh Maria dulu<br/>sebab dia dapat tahu</p>
<p begin="51955600000t" end="51981020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle968">rahsia aku dengan bapa dia, Pak Osman.</p>
<p begin="51984770000t" end="52006020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle969">Aku tak sangka Pak Osman mati, Adam.</p>
<p begin="52006850000t" end="52033930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle970">Kau tahu tak<br/>berapa ramai yang mati sebab kau?</p>
<p begin="52038930000t" end="52066020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle971">Kau pentingkan diri kau sendiri,</p>
<p begin="52070180000t" end="52086850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle972">bukan sebab agama.</p>
<p begin="52088520000t" end="52105600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle973">Kau nak semua orang hormat kau.</p>
<p begin="52107680000t" end="52118520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle974">Itu yang kau nak.</p>
<p begin="52121020000t" end="52133520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle975">Bukan sebab pahala.</p>
<p begin="52136020000t" end="52161020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle976">Sepatutnya orang sanjung aku, Adam.</p>
<p begin="52169350000t" end="52196020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle977">Sepatutnya aku berada di tempat kau.</p>
<p begin="52209770000t" end="52218100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle978">Kau faham?</p>
<p begin="52221430000t" end="52261430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle979">Nafsu syaitan dan hasad<br/>dah masuk dalam jiwa kau, Azman!</p>
<p begin="52273520000t" end="52283520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle980">Kau kalah!</p>
<p begin="52285180000t" end="52298520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle981">Kau itu yang kalah, Adam.</p>
<p begin="52303100000t" end="52316850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle982">Kau itu anak derhaka.</p>
<p begin="52320600000t" end="52330600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle983">Kau tengok ini!</p>
<p begin="52332680000t" end="52354350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle984">Ayah kau sendiri pun<br/>kau tak mampu nak jaga.</p>
<p begin="52369350000t" end="52398930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle985">Aku tahu semua kisah silam kau, Adam.</p>
<p begin="52399770000t" end="52427270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle986">Anak isteri kau mati<br/>sebab Tuhan dah tak terima kau.</p>
<p begin="52440600000t" end="52461430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle987">Tapi kau jangan risau.</p>
<p begin="52465180000t" end="52484770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle988">Kau akan jumpa dengan mereka.</p>
<p begin="52488930000t" end="52536020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle989">Anak isteri kau itu sedang menangis<br/>menunggu kau di pintu neraka!</p>
<p begin="52703930000t" end="52727270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle990">Kau lah penunggang agama, Adam!</p>
<p begin="52728100000t" end="52739770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle991">Bukan aku!</p>
<p begin="52746020000t" end="52757270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle992">Golongan dajjal!</p>
<p begin="52796850000t" end="52820600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle993">Golongan dajjal pendusta!</p>
<p begin="52966430000t" end="52975600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle994">Adam!</p>
<p begin="52982680000t" end="53024770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle995">Siapa dajjal, Adam?<br/>Kau lah musuh Allah dan Rasul!</p>
<p begin="53033520000t" end="53057680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle996">Kau lah golongan dajjal akhir zaman!</p>
<p begin="53059770000t" end="53078100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle997">Mesti dihukum mati!</p>
<p begin="53250600000t" end="53263930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle998">Adam!</p>
<p begin="53271430000t" end="53283100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle999">Ayah...</p>
<p begin="53406430000t" end="53418520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1000">Demi Allah!</p>
<p begin="53419350000t" end="53437270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1001">Kau ikut telunjuk syaitan, Abuja.</p>
<p begin="53438520000t" end="53466850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1002">Apakah kau jadikan Iblis<br/>sebagai sekutu Allah!</p>
<p begin="53468930000t" end="53497270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1003">Kita hamba, kita zuriat Adam.</p>
<p begin="53501430000t" end="53514770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1004">Bukan zuriat Iblis!</p>
<p begin="53524350000t" end="53547680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1005">Aku tak nak kau tazkirah dekat sini!</p>
<p begin="53554350000t" end="53571850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1006">Jangan nak samakan aku dengan kau!</p>
<p begin="53578100000t" end="53608100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1007">Orang yang takbur dan sombong</p>
<p begin="53611850000t" end="53626850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1008">untuk beribadah kepada Allah,</p>
<p begin="53638100000t" end="53648100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1009">macam kau</p>
<p begin="53657680000t" end="53676020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1010">akan masuk ke neraka Jahannam!</p>
<p begin="53689350000t" end="53718100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1011">Dalam keadaan hina, azab yang pedih.</p>
<p begin="53776430000t" end="53788520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1012">Kau yang hina!</p>
<p begin="53805180000t" end="53823520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1013">Siapa kau nak cakap macam itu?</p>
<p begin="53826850000t" end="53841850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1014">Siapa kau nak hukum aku?</p>
<p begin="53842680000t" end="53874350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1015">Tiada yg lebih sesat daripada org<br/>menyeru selain daripada Allah.</p>
<p begin="53875180000t" end="53888520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1016">Tidak!</p>
<p begin="53890180000t" end="53936850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1017">Syaitan Iblis yang kau puja dan sembah<br/>akan jadi musuh kau sendiri.</p>
<p begin="53941850000t" end="53954350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1018">Sampai hari kiamat.</p>
<p begin="53966850000t" end="53978100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1019">Sampai kiamat!</p>
<p begin="54003100000t" end="54014770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1020">Adam!</p>
<p begin="54058930000t" end="54071430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1021">Abuja!</p>
<p begin="54078520000t" end="54100600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1022">Aku merayu kepada kau,</p>
<p begin="54103100000t" end="54139350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1023">janganlah diseksa dia lagi. Ya Allah...</p>
<p begin="54143100000t" end="54179350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1024">Cukuplah kau menzalimi anak aku!</p>
<p begin="54181850000t" end="54194770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1025">Jangan merayu kepada dia.</p>
<p begin="54205180000t" end="54216430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1026">Dia tak layak.</p>
<p begin="54228930000t" end="54243100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1027">Merayu kepada Allah.</p>
<p begin="54258930000t" end="54269760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1028">Doa, Ayah.</p>
<p begin="54272680000t" end="54281850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1029">Yakin, Ayah.</p>
<p begin="54286850000t" end="54326850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1030">Manusia macam kau<br/>Allah takkan terima lagi doa.</p>
<p begin="54327680000t" end="54355180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1031">Sebab hati kau gelap dan lalai!</p>
<p begin="54522270000t" end="54563100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1032">Aku nak tengok sejauh mana<br/>kau cintakan Nabi dan ahlul bait.</p>
<p begin="54566850000t" end="54587680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1033">Apa yang kau dapat dari semua ini?</p>
<p begin="54588930000t" end="54629350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1034">Tak ada apa-apa,<br/>kecuali azab dunia yang pedih!</p>
<p begin="54630180000t" end="54656850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1035">Aku dah tak peduli,<br/>selagi agama aku selamat.</p>
<p begin="54658930000t" end="54672270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1036">Makhluk tiada kuasa.</p>
<p begin="54682270000t" end="54697270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1037">Allah yang berkuasa.</p>
